{
  "_comment": "ComfyUI IPAdapter (character transplant, Doc 14 mode=character). KSampler model fed by the IPAdapter-patched model (13). Reference image loaded at node 10. weight 0.8 = balanced character likeness (tunable, Doc 14 §7).",
